<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Promise
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">对象表示异步操作的最终完成（或失败）及其结果值</span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Promise
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">是在创建</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> Promise
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">时不一定知道的值的代理。它允许您将处理程序与异步操作的最终成功值或失败原因相关联。这让异步方法像同步方法一样返回值：异步方法不是立即返回最终值，而是返回一个承诺，以在未来的某个时间提供该值。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">Promise
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">处于以下状态之一：</span></span>
        <ol style="list-style-type:decimal">
            <li value="1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">pending</span></span> <span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">初始状态，既不满足也不拒绝。</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">fulfilled</span></span> <span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表示操作成功完成</span></span></li>
            <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">rejected</span></span> <span
                    style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                        style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表示操作失败</span></span></li>
        </ol>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">pending
                promise</span></span> <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的最终状态可以用一个值来实现（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">fulfilled</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">），也可以用一个原因（错误）拒绝（</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">rejected</span></span>
        <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">）。当这些选项中的任何一个发生时，将调用由</span></span><span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> promise
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">的</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> then </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">方法排队的相关处理程序。如果在附加相应的处理程序时承诺已经被履行或拒绝，则处理程序将被调用，因此异步操作完成与其附加处理程序之间没有竞争条件。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">如果一个</span></span>
        <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">promise</span></span>
        <span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">被履行或被拒绝，但不是待处理的，则称该</span></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">promise</span></span> <span
            style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">已解决。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>

                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> onFulfilled </span><span

                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> onRejected </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">不是函数），则返回其原始结算值</span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span

                <p><span style="font-size:11.5pt"><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">将处理程序附加到</span><span
